game.name: Goldie Princess Mommy Birth
game.description:
The cute princess Goldie is pregnant and expected to deliver a baby soon. She cannot handle the stress caused by the labor pain on her own so the lady needs your help. Join Goldie Princess Mommy Birth game and be prepared to provide her with the needful medical assistance to enjoy a hassle-free pregnancy experience! Pick up a phone and dial 911 to call the ambulance! Try to take care of her until the ambulance arrives to her home as a doctor!
Remember is in labor pain so it is important to keep her comfortable until she reaches to the hospital in this HTML5 medical simulation game. Give her a nice and comfortable night gown and call Flynn from time to time to pamper the pregnant lady with the lovely kiss! Do not forget to use a glass of water to keep the girl hydrated in this cool doctor game. Make sure that she continues taking a proper breathe. In case of shortage of oxygen, give her an oxygen mask. It looks now she is ready to go to the hospital. 
In the hospital, she gives birth to a cute baby. After the delivery, try to wipe out all the sweat Goldie and the little baby sweat. You have to cut the umbilical cord with soft hands in the next step. Now measure the weight of her baby and then give him the nice baby powder and change his diapers. Use the blanket then to wrap him up properly in this baby caring simulation game! Give some vitamins to Goldie and take care of her baby as well by feeding him with the breast milk! Enjoy more pregnant games for girls and have a blast without download!
